%20written%20complaint%20against%20Swati%20Maliwal%2C%20alleging%20unauthorized%20entry%2C%20verbal%20abuse%2C%20and%20threats%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20BJP%20hand%20behind%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%20lodged%20by%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20addressed%20to%20the%20SHO%20Civil%20Lines%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20reportedly%20%26quot%3Bforcefully%20and%20illegally%20trespassed%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20chief%20minister%20residence%20despite%20objections%20from%20the%20chief%20minister's%20security%20and%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20claimed%20that%20Swati%20Maliwal%2C%20upon%20being%20asked%20to%20take%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20hurled%20abuses%20at%20him%20and%20disregarded%20the%20security%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaliwal%20started%20screaming%20and%20shouting%2C%20hurling%20abuses%2C%20and%20questioning%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20security%20personnel%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20Mr%20Kumar%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20motives%20were%20suspect%2C%20and%20she%20intended%20to%20harm%20the%20Hon'ble%20chief%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReportedly%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20made%20threats%20against%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BMain%20tujhe%20dekh%20lungi...main%20tujhe%20aese%20joothe%20case%20mei%20fasaungi%20ki%20tujhe%20zindagi%20bhar%20jail%20mei%20sadah%20dungi%26quot%3B%20(%26quot%3BI%20will%20make%20sure%20you%20face%20consequences%3B%20I%20will%20ensure%20you%20rot%20in%20jail%20for%20life%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20officers%20were%20called%20to%20intervene%2C%20and%20after%20repeated%20requests%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20finally%20left%20the%20premises%20around%209%3A35%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20urged%20authorities%20to%20take%20appropriate%20legal%20action%20against%20Swati%20Maliwal%20and%20requested%20an%20investigation%20into%20her%20possible%20ties%20with%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20suggesting%20political%20motives%20behind%20the%20incident%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20Ms%20Maliwal%20has%20made%20unauthorised%20entry%2C%20trespassed%2C%20breached%20the%20security%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20Residence%2C%20prevented%20government%20officers%20from%20discharging%20their%20duty%20and%20assaulted%20the%20complainant%2C%20she%20is%20liable%20for%20her%20action%20as%20per%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20requested%20to%20take%20appropriate%20legal%20action%20against%20Ms%20Maliwal.%20Since%20it%20is%20election%20time%2C%20all%20of%20this%20may%20have%20been%20done%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20it%20is%20therefore%20requested%20that%20her%20call%20records%2C%20chats%20and%20interactions%20with%20BJP%20leaders%20should%20also%20be%20investigated%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20added%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20assistant%20comes%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20Swati%20Maliwal's%20complaint%20against%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20of%20assaulting%20her%20at%20chief%20minister's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20filed%20an%20FIR%20in%20the%20case%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20Swati%20Maliwal%20and%20the%20details%20of%20the%20FIR%20have%20revealed%20shocking%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20has%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20Secretary%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20%26quot%3Bslapped%26quot%3B%20her%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20seven%20to%20eight%20times%26quot%3B%20while%20she%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20screaming%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbrutally%20dragged%26quot%3B%20her%20while%20%26quot%3Bkicking%26quot%3B%20her%20in%20her%20%26quot%3Bchest%2C%20stomach%20and%20pelvis%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20FIR%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20described%20the%20events%20of%20May%2013%20when%20she%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20Civil%20Lines%20residence%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20inside%20the%20camp%20office%20and%20called%20chief%20minister's%20PS%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20but%20I%20could%20not%20go%20in.%20I%20then%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20his%20mobile%20number%20(through%20WhatsApp).%20However%2C%20there%20was%20no%20response.%20I%20then%20went%20inside%20the%20residential%20area%20through%20the%20main%20door%20as%20I%20have%20always%20done%20in%20the%20past%20year%20since%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20was%20not%20present%20I%20entered%20the%20residence%20area%20and%20informed%20the%20staff%20present%20there%20to%20tell%20the%20chief%20minister%20here%20to%20meet%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FIR%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20present%20in%20the%20house%20and%20I%20was%20told%20to%20wait%20in%20the%20drawing%20room.%20I%20went%20into%20the%20drawing%20room%20and%20sat%20on%20the%20sofa%20and%20waited%20for%20him%20to%20meet%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Maliwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20then%20abused%20me%20and%20asked%20who%20are%20you%20to%20not%20listen%20to%20what%20I%20say.%20While%20saying%20these%20words%2C%20he%20came%20and%20stood%20right%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20Without%20any%20provocation%20whatsoever%20on%20my%20side%2C%20he%20started%20slapping%20me%20with%20full%20force.%20He%20slapped%20me%20seven%20to%20eight%20times%20at%20least%20while%20I%20continued%20screaming.%20I%20felt%20absolutely%20shocked%20and%20was%20screaming%20for%20help%20over%20and%20over%20again.%20In%20order%20to%20protect%20myself%20I%20pushed%20him%20away%20with%20my%20legs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20repeatedly%20told%20him...that%20he%20should%20please%20let%20go%20of%20me%20as%20I%20was%20in%20unbearable%20pain.%20However%2C%20he%20attacked%20me%20with%20full%20force%20again%20and%20again.%20I%20somehow%20managed%20to%20get%20free.%20I%20