20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Vigilance%20Department%20had%20last%20month%20terminated%20the%20service%20of%20Bibhav%20Kumar%2C%20personal%20assistant%20(PA)%20to%20Delhi%20CM%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20over%20a%20pending%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20written%20complaint%20to%20the%20SHO%20of%20Civil%20Lines%20Police%20Station%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20urged%20authorities%20to%20take%20appropriate%20legal%20action%20against%20Ms%20Maliwal%20and%20requested%20an%20investigation%20into%20her%20possible%20ties%20with%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20suggesting%20political%20motives%20behind%20the%20incident%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20complaint%20came%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20Swati%20Maliwal's%20allegations%20against%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20for%20'assaulting'%20her%20at%20the%20CM's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20attacked%20Ms%20Maliwal%20on%20Friday%20over%20a%20purported%20video%20clip%20from%20the%20CM's%20residence%20that%20was%20supposedly%20taken%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20alleged%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20posted%20by%20a%20news%20channel%2C%20was%20shared%20by%20the%20party%20with%20a%20caption%20that%20read%20%26quot%3BSwati%20Maliwal%20ka%20sach%20(Swati%20Maliwal's%20truth).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20purportedly%20showed%20Maliwal%20having%20an%20argument%20with%20the%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20CM's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20AAP%20has%20taken%20a%20stand%20against%20Ms%20Maliwal%20in%20the%20case%2C%20contradicting%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20statement%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20has%20directed%20%26quot%3Bstrict%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20party%20is%20%26quot%3Bwith%20Swati%20Maliwal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20filed%20an%20FIR%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20Ms%20Maliwal%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20alleged%20that%20Kejriwal's%20aide%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%2C%20%26quot%3Bslapped%26quot%3B%20her%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20seven%20to%20eight%20times%26quot%3B%20while%20she%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20screaming%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbrutally%20dragged%26quot%3B%20her%20while%20%26quot%3Bkicking%26quot%3B%20her%20in%20her%20%26quot%3Bchest%2C%20stomach%2C%20and%20pelvis%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20FIR%2C%20Swati%20Maliwal%20described%20the%20events%20of%20May%2013%20when%20she%20went%20to%20the%20Civil%20Lines%20residence%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20row%20over%20the%20alleged%20assault%20on%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20intensified%2C%20Swati%20Maliwal%20attacked%20her%20party%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20saving%20a%20%26quot%3BGunda%26quot%3B%20(hitman)%20and%20indulging%20in%20her%20%26quot%3Bcharacter%20assassination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Maliwal's%20response%20came%20soon%20after%20a%20press%20conference%20by%20AAP%20leader%20Atishi%2C%20where%20she%20termed%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP's%20visit%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20residence%20as%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20an%20apparent%20jibe%20at%20Atishi%2C%20Maliwal%20stated%20in%20her%20post%2C%20%26quot%3Bkal%20ke%20aaye%20neta%26quot%3B%20(leaders%20who%20joined%20the%20party%20yesterday)%2C%20while%20drawing%20comparisons%20with%20her%20long%20association%20with%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20MP%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20her%20party%20had%20initially%20accepted%20the%20assault%20against%20her%2C%20they%20have%20now%20taken%20a%20%26quot%3BU-turn%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20Tis%20Hazari%20court%20recorded%20the%20statement%20of%20Swati%20Maliwal%20in%20the%20assault%20case%20on%20Friday.%20An%20FIR%20ha