ore%20vibrant%20democracies%20in%20the%20world%20than%20India.%20And%20we%20applaud%20the%20Indian%20people%20for%20exercising%2C%20you%20know%2C%20their%20ability%20to%20vote%2C%20and%20to%20have%20a%20voice%20in%20their%20future%20government.%20And%20we%20wish%20them%20well%20throughout%20the%20process%2C%20of%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Communications%20Advisor%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20news%20conference%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirby%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20elections%2C%20wherein%20over%20969%20million%20people%20are%20exercising%20their%20right%20to%20franchise%20at%20one%20million%20polling%20stations%20to%20elect%20545%20members%20of%20parliament%20from%20thousands%20of%20candidates%20representing%20as%20many%20as%202%2C660%20registered%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20another%20question%2C%20Kirby%20said%20the%20India-US%20relationship%20has%20strengthened%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20particular%20during%20the%20last%20three%20years%20of%20the%20Biden%20administration.%20%26quot%3BOur%20relationship%20with%20India%20is%20extremely%20close%20and%20getting%20closer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20saw%20it%20on%20a%20State%20visit%20(last%20visit).%20We%20launched%20all%20kinds%20of%20new%20initiatives%2C%20working%20on%20critical%20emerging%20technologies%20together%2C%20and%20bolstering%20and%20expanding%20the%20relevance%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20quad%2C%20of%20course%2C%20which%20India%20is%20a%20part%20of.%20And%20then%2C%20just%20the%20people%20to%20people%20exchanges%2C%20and%20the%20military%20that%20we%20share%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20vibrant%2C%20very%20active%20partnership.%20We%20are%20grateful%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20White%20House%20official.%3C%2Fp%