e%20good%20news%20is%20that%20Google%20Pay%20is%20free%20to%20use.%20The%20Google%20Pay%20and%20Google%20Wallet%20apps%20are%20free%20to%20download%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20subscription%20or%20service%20fee%20to%20use%20the%20service%20to%20make%20mobile%20payments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20purchases%20you%20make%20with%20Google%20Pay%20are%20completely%20free.%20Google%20Pay%20lets%20you%20make%20payments%20through%20your%20credit%20cards%2C%20debit%20cards%2C%20and%20bank%20accounts%2C%20so%20if%20you%20would%20ordinarily%20pay%20interest%20or%20a%20fee%20when%20using%20a%20card%2C%20you'll%20still%20pay%20that%20fee%20when%20using%20it%20through%20Google%20Pay.%20You%20simply%20won't%20pay%20anything%20additional%20for%20the%20privilege%20of%20using%20Google%20Pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf2e2d37-ae03-46bb-88a6-715a1db4d322%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%20Pay%20is%20safe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20Google%20Pay%20is%20safer%20and%20more%20secure%20than%20using%20a%20credit%20card%2C%20and%20for%20a%20number%20of%20reasons.%20First%20and%20foremost%3A%20Google%20Pay%20purchases%20are%20tokenized%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20service%20sends%20your%20credit%20information%20using%20a%20unique%20code%20for%20each%20purchase.%20If%20the%20information%20could%20be%20intercepted%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20useful%20to%20a%20thief%20or%20hacker%2C%20because%20your%20credit%20card%20information%20isn't%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20even%20more%20important%2C%20though%2C%20is%20the%20physical%20security%20that%20Google%20Pay%20offers.%20If%20your%20actual%20credit%20card%20is%20lost%20or%20stolen%2C%20it%20can%20potentially%20be%20used%20to%20make%20purchases%2C%20at%20least%20until%20you%20notify%20the%20credit%20company%20and%20cancel%20the%20card.%20But%20when%20using%20Google%20Pay%20on%20your%20phone%2C%20your%20credit%20card%20information%20is%20protected%20behind%20a%20passcode%20or%20biometrics%20like%20facial%20recognition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a1da198-a565-4250-9a51-57855ea7332f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20using%20Google%20Pay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20her%20smartphone%20up%20to%20a%20payment%20reader%20to%20make%20a%20contactless%20payment.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d90b31caec1275a706870%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENot%20all%20retailers%20accept%20Google%20Pay.%20Small%20businesses%20and%20independent%20stores%20may%20still%20require%20your%20physical%20credit%20or%20debit%20card.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20advantage%20of%20Google%20Pay%20is%20that%20it's%20integrated%20with%20a%20number%20of%20other%20popular%20Google%20products.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-flights-price-guarantee-program-money-back-refund-fares-increase-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20a%20price%20guarantee%20where%20Google%20will%20pay%20you%20the%20difference%20if%20the%20price%20of%20your%20flight%20drops%20after%20you%20book%20it%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20have%20to%20have%20a%20Google%20Pay%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20there%20are%20both%20pros%20and%20cons%20to%20using%20Google%20Pay.%20Not%20only%20is%20Google%20Pay%20a%20safe%20and%20secure%20payment%20system%2C%20but%20it's%20broadly%20compatible%20with%20many%20retail%20stores%20%E2%80%94%20just%20look%20for%20the%20Google%20Pay%20or%20tap-to-pay%20symbol%20at%20checkout.%20And%20via%20the%20Google%20Wallet%20app%2C%20Google%20Pay%20does%20a%20lot%20more%2C%20letting%20you%20store%20transit%20cards%20and%20boarding%20passes%2C%20loyalty%20cards%2C%20and%20more%20all%20in%20one%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20there%20are%20some%20disadvantages%20to%20Google%20Pay%20as%20well.%20As%20pervasive%20as%20Google%20Pay%20is%20at%20retailers%2C%20especially%20in%20large%20cities%2C%20it's%20far%20from%20ubiquitous.%20Especially%20in%20smaller%20locales%20and%20at%20independent%20stores%2C%20you%20might%20have%20trouble%20using%20Google%20Pay%20to%20make%20purchases.%20That%20means%20you%20still%20need%20to%20carry%20a%20physical%20credit%20card%2C%20at%20least%20as%20a%20backup%2C%20which%20can%20defeat%20the%20purpose%20of%20using%20Google%20Pay%20to%20begin%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20forthcoming%20end%20of%20the%20Google%20Pay%20app%2C%20Google%20is%20also%20leaving%20Apple%20users%20out%20in%20the%20cold.%20That%20means%20Google%20Pay%20could%20be%20an%20Android-only%20service%20starting%20in%20June%202024%2C%20unless%20Google%20releases%20a%20Google%20Wallet%20app%20for%20the%20iPhone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-pay%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715988541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661d937b1caec1275a706fb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-pay%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20Pay%20is%20a%20digital%20payment%20service%20that%20you%20can%20use%20to%20make%20contactless%20mobile%20payments.%20Here's%20how%20to%20use%20it%2C%20potential%20disadvantages%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Dave%20Johnson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-pay%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nike%20Releases%20New%20Air%20Jordan%2011%20Retro%20Low%20Sneakers%3A%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Where%20to%20Get%20A%20Pair%20Online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715988060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2