ips%20on%20the%20high%20seas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221083%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20French%20helicopter%20shot%20down%20a%20Houthi%20attack%20drone%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%20March.%20Houthi%20rebels%20have%20since%20used%20their%20UAVs%20to%20threaten%20ships%20far%20beyond%20the%20Red%20Sea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647c7a314fb5b23cc5e0563%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20French%20helicopter%20shot%20down%20a%20Houthi%20attack%20drone%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%20March.%20Houthi%20rebels%20have%20since%20used%20their%20UAVs%20to%20threaten%20ships%20far%20beyond%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3Cp%3EFrench%20Army%2FHandout%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECommercial%20ships%20have%20diverted%20from%20the%20Red%20Sea%20over%20the%20Houthi%20missile%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Houthis%20showed%20in%20late%20April%20they%20can%20strike%20ships%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BBy%20disrupting%20shipping%2C%20the%20Houthis%20can%20impose%20costs%20on%20the%20global%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20naval%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHouthi%20militants%20showed%20in%20late%20April%20that%20they%20can%20expand%20their%20war%20on%20international%20shipping%20far%20beyond%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20container%20ship%20MSC%20Orion%20came%20under%20a%20drone%20attack%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lloydslist.com%2FLL1149009%2FHouthis-deploy-new-weapons-to-secure-first-direct-hit-in-Indian-Ocean%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enight%20of%20April%2026%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20it%20was%20steaming%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20southeast%20of%20the%20Horn%20of%20Africa%2C%20the%20continent's%20eastern-most%20tip.%20The%20attack%20only%20caused%20minor%20damage%20and%20did%20not%20harm%20any%20crew.%20But%20the%20distance%20involved%20was%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Houthis%20have%20wreaked%20havoc%20against%20international%20shipping%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20with%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20exploding%20drones%2C%20and%20threatened%20in%20March%20they%20could%20menace%20ships%20that%20avoided%20this%20route%20by%20going%20around%20Africa's%20southern%20Cape%20of%20Good%20Hope%2C%20a%20much%20longer%20and%20more%20expensive%20voyage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Houthis%20have%20drones%20that%20can%20travel%20more%20than%201%2C000%20nautical%20miles%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Shahed%20series%20of%20propellor-driven%20drones%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryan%20Clark%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Hudson%20Institute%20and%20expert%20on%20naval%20operations%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20ballistic%20missiles%20have%20ranges%20of%20more%20than%20600%20%5Bnautical%20miles%5D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20long-range%20attack%20on%20the%20Orion%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20a%20one-off%20but%20is%20still%20unprecedented%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20drone%20warfare%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20attack%20was%20different%20in%20the%20fact%20it%20was%20achieved%20over%20a%20greater%20distance%20than%20previous%20attacks%20on%20international%20shipping%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Patton%20Rogers%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Cornell%20Tech%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20shows%20advances%20in%20range%2C%20command%20and%20control%2C%20and%20accuracy%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20occurring%20despite%20US-UK%20efforts%20to%20degrade%20the%20group.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERogers%20believes%20the%20Houthis%20may%20have%20used%20a%20long-range%20Shehab%20drone%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20now%2C%20the%20Shehab%20drones%20have%20proven%20vulnerable%20to%20air%20defense%20and%20unreliable%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20such%2C%20if%20Shehab%20drones%20were%20used%20in%20the%20strikes%2C%20which%20the%20video%20evidence%20appears%20to%20show%2C%20then%20it%20would%20mark%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20reliability%20and%20destructive%20precision%20of%20these%20drone%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20noted%20that%20the%20Shehab's%20reported%20range%20of%20990%20miles%20puts%20it%20%26quot%3Bwell%20within%20range%26quot%3B%20of%20international%20shipping.%20The%20US%20and%20EU%20have%20stood%20up%20naval%20task%20forces%20to%20guard%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20but%20merchant%20ships%20far%20outside%20of%20these%20air%20defense%20umbrellas%20have%20no%20defense%20against%20an%20attack%20drone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYet%20these%20are%20not%20the%20only%20systems%20available%20to%20the%20so-called'%20axis%20of%20resistance'%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Samad%20(1500km%2F932%20miles)%20and%20potentially%20the%20Shahed%20(2000km)%20family%20of%20drones%20all%20have%20the%20range%20to%20strike%20these%20targets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20British-registered%20cargo%20ship%20'Rubymar'%20sank%20in%20March%20after%20it%20was%20targeted%20by%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20forces%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647c9f59fc063e829b29790%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22647%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20British-registered%20cargo%20ship%20'Rubymar'%20sank%20in%20March%20after%20it%20was%20targeted%20by%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20forces%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Hamoud%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESearching%20and%20targeting%20ships%20in%20international%20waters%20is%20also%20another%20escalation%20from%20the%20group's%20attacks%20near%20the%20Red%20Sea.%20The%20Houthis%20are%20most%20likely%20exploiting%20the%20self-reporting%20of%20merchant%20ships%20to%20target%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Houthis%20appear%20to%20be%20using%20AIS%20(Automatic%20Identification%20System)%20data%20to%20geolocate%20their%20targets%20and%20use%20GPS%20to%20guide%20their%20drone%20to%20the%20approximate%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20%26quot%3BReportedly%2C%20drones%20like%20the%20Shahed%20series%20have%20anti-radiation%20seekers%20they%20can%20use%20to%20drive%20into%20emitting%20targets%20like%20air%20defense%20radars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Orion%20stopped%20transmitting%20its%20AIS%20after%20the%20April%2026%20attack%2C%20likely%20to%20prevent%20the%20Houthis%20from%20tracking%20the%20ship%20for%20a%20second%20strike.%20Clark%20also%20believes%20ships%20like%20the%20Orion%20may%20opt%20for%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20dark%26quot%3B%20for%20segments%20of%20their%20voyage%20to%20avoid%20being%20tracked.%20Ships%20smuggling%20Russian%20oil%20have%20done%20this%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20current%20Ukraine%20war%20in%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20some%20ways%20these%20ships%20can%20evade%20such%20attacks%20or%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%20physically%20fend%20them%20off.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThey%20could%20turn%20off%20their%20AIS%20and%20radar%2C%20which%20would%20make%20them%20hard%20to%20find%20in%20the%20open%20ocean%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Mediterranean%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20they%20enter%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20though%2C%20ships%20can%20be%20tracked%20by%20spotters%20ashore%20or%20on%20boats%20or%20using%20mobile%20Houthi%20radars%20ashore.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20shotguns%20or%20high-power%20microwave%20counter-drone%20weapons%20would%20be%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShips%20may%20opt%20for%20alternative%20or%20longer%20routes%20to%20avoid%20these%20attacks%2C%20and%20while%20this%20may%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20attacks%2C%20that%20would%20also%20have%20a%20disruptive%20impact%20on%20shipping%20of%20the%20kind%20the%20Houthis%20would%20welcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20easiest%2C%20although%20more%20expensive%2C%20way%20to%20address%20this%20threat%20is%20to%20avoid%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20that%20is%20what%20the%20Houthis%20want.%20By%20disrupting%20shipping%2C%20the%20Houthis%20can%20impose%20costs%20on%20the%20global%20economy%20and%20put%20pressure%20on%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20forces%20targeting%20the%20Houthis%20in%20February%20encountered%20an%20undersea%20drone%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F02%2F19%2Fus-houthi-strike-underwater-drone-red-sea%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20successfully%20struck%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20few%20details%20about%20the%20Houthi's%20underwater%20drone%20capacity%2C%20but%20what%20there%20is%20suggests%20the%20drones%20are%20slow-moving%20and%20more%20useful%20against%20stationary%20targets%2C%20ships%20vulnerable%20in%20dock%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%20%26quot%3BNevertheless%2C%20with%20the%20rate%20of%20Houthi%20advances%2C%20and%20increases%20in%20speed%2C%20control%2C%20and%20maneuverability%20in-transit%2C%20international%20shipping%20could%20soon%20prove%20vulnerable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClark%20doesn't%20see%20undersea%20drones%20posing%20much%20of%20a%20threat%20to%20ships%20on%20the%20high%20seas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BUndersea%20drones%20are%20really%20only%20a%20threat%20in%20narrow%20waters%20like%20the%20Red%20Sea%20where%20the%20range%20to%20shore%20is%20short%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20%26quot%3BUndersea%20drones%20can%20only%20travel%20a%20few%20knots%20and%20therefore%20cannot%20catch%20up%20to%20a%20cargo%20ship.%20The%20drone%20has%20to%20intercept%20the%20target%2C%20which%20requires%20knowing%20where%20the%20target%20is%20going%2C%20such%20as%20in%20a%20narrow%20waterway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERogers%20believes%20the%20broader%20implications%20of%20the%20Orion%20attack%20are%20already%20clear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BViolent%20non-state%20groups%20are%20not%20only%20able%20to%20strike%20shipping%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20from%20shore%2C%20but%20they%20are%20able%20to%20pass%20this%20technology%20on%20to%20other%20groups%20allied%20with%20the%20cause%20or%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIn%20essence%2C%20we%20have%20reached%20a%20stage%20where%20the%20proliferation%20of%20this%20capacity%20is%20uncontrolled%20and%20unchecked%2C%20potentially%20bringing%20international%20shipping%20and%20global%20supply%20chains%20under%20increased%20threat%20globally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-are-menacing-ships-on-the-high-seas-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715986861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647c89714fb5b23cc5e05c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-are-menacing-ships-on-the-high-seas-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Houthis%20have%20wreaked%20havoc%20against%20international%20shipping%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20are%20showing%20they%20can%20still%20attack%20ships%20that%20try%20to%20avoid%20the%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Paul%20Iddon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin