es-Authentic-Handcrafted%252Fdp%252FB0007D6GS0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20overall%5C%22%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20the%20HexClad%20Damascus%20Steel%20Serrated%20Bread%20Knife%20as%20our%20best%20overall%20pick%20because%20it%20hit%20the%20mark%20for%20quality%2C%20value%2C%20and%20performance.%20This%20knife's%20performance%20surprised%20us%20by%20feeling%20just%20as%20balanced%20and%20cutting%20just%20as%20well%20as%20the%20more%20expensive%20options%20we%20tested.%20And%20that's%20likely%20all%20thanks%20to%20its%2067%20layers%20of%20Japanese%20Damascus%20steel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20the%20typical%20wide%20serrations%20found%20on%20most%20bread%20knife%20blades%2C%20HexClad%20opted%20for%20finer%2C%20pointer%20teeth%20to%20create%20a%20faster%2C%20smoother%20cut.%20Celebrity%20chef%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgochahawkins%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGocha%20Hawkins%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20us%20that%20if%20you%20want%20to%20test%20a%20knife's%20sharpness%2C%20you%20should%20see%20how%20it%20cuts%20through%20a%20tomato.%20If%20it%20slides%20right%20through%20without%20crushing%20the%20fruit%2C%20it's%20a%20winner.%20The%20HexClad%20passed%20this%20test%20with%20flying%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22HexClad%20Bread%20Knife%20cutting%20a%20loaf%20of%20bread.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664616dd9fc063e829b1a5c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20HexClad%20knife's%20has%20sharp%20teeth%20and%20medium%20troughs%20that%20slices%20through%20bread%20crust%20and%20delicate%20fruit.%3Cp%3EM8nshot%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20we%20do%20wish%20it%20came%20with%20a%20sheath%20for%20safety%20purposes%2C%20considering%20its%20affordability%2C%20impressive%20blade%20performance%2C%20and%20nicely%20balanced%20Pakkawood%20handle%2C%20we%20can't%20complain%20too%20much.%20Plus%2C%20its%2060%20Rockwell%20Hardness%20Rating%20indicates%20decent%20durability%20and%20sharpness%20retention%2C%20which%20are%20necessary%20two%20qualities%20for%20a%20long-lasting%20bread%20knife.%20We're%20big%20fans%20of%20the%20HexClad%20brand%3A%20read%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-nonstick-cookware-sets%5C%22%3Ebest%20nonstick%20cookware%3C%2Fa%3E%20(featuring%20a%20HexClad%20set)%20if%20you%20need%20to%20upgrade%20your%20cookware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20love%20all%20the%20knives%20on%20this%20list%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20spend%20%24100%20to%20get%20a%20reliable%20bread%20knife.%20Mercer%20Culinary%20has%20a%20few%20budget-friendly%20lines%20(like%20the%20Millennia%20and%20Renaissance%20collections)%20that%20outperform%20pricier%20alternatives.%20Straight%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20this%20knife%20cuts%20just%20as%20well%20as%20any%20of%20our%20top%20picks.%20You%20can%20even%20match%20this%20knife%20to%20kitchen%20tools%20you%20already%20have%3A%20there%20are%20five%20available%20handle%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Millenia%20Bread%20Knife%20is%20lightweight%2C%20in%20part%20thanks%20to%20the%20Santoprene%20handle.%20We%20sliced%20through%20fragile%20tomatoes%20and%20ripe%20strawberries%20without%20crushing%20the%20delicate%20flesh%2C%20and%20we%20weren't%20foiled%20by%20stale%2C%20crusty%20bread.%20The%20Millenia%20Bread%20Knife%20has%20a%20rounded%20tip%2C%20which%20helps%20create%20a%20smooth%20slice%2C%20but%20leaves%20you%20unable%20to%20pierce%20tough%20skins%20or%20rinds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20HRC%20of%2054%2C%20the%20Millenia%20knives%20are%20on%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20edge%20retention%20and%20wear%20resistance.%20Essentially%2C%20you'll%20probably%20have%20to%20sharpen%20this%20knife%20more%20frequently%20than%20one%20of%20the%20tougher%20knives%20we%20highlight.%20The%20Millenia%20Bread%20knife%20isn't%20a%20legacy%20piece%20that%20you'll%20hand%20down%20to%20future%20generations%20of%20breadbakers%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20best%20bread%20knife%20for%20today's%20budget-minded%20sandwich%20eaters.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3ELily%20Alig%2C%20Kitchen%20Editor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20upgrade%5C%22%3EBest%20upgrade%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Steelport%20Bread%20Knife%20is%20truly%20a%20cut%20above%20the%20rest.%20Most%20blades%20of%20this%20kind%20have%20a%20traditional%20pointed%20serration%20that%20catches%20the%20bread's%20crust%20to%20slice%20it%2C%20but%20the%20Steelport's%20blade%20is%20wavy.%20Out%20of%20all%20the%20knives%20we%20tested%2C%20we%20found%20that%20this%20distinctive%20serration%20made%20for%20the%20nicest%20pull%2C%20cutting%20even%20the%20most%20well-stocked%20sandwiches%20as%20smoothly%20as%20butter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20helping%20its%20slicing%20abilities%20is%20the%20ergonomic%20handle%20made%20with%20locally%20sourced%20Oregon%20big-leaf%20maple%20burl%20wood.%20We%20thought%20it%20felt%20heavy%20without%20being%20cumbersome%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20comfortable%20grip%20that%20requires%20minimal%20force%20to%20slice%20through%20the%20crustiest%20of%20loaves.%20The%20handle%20even%20has%20a%20built-in%20notch%20for%20your%20index%20finger%20to%20rest%20in%20while%20you're%20making%20quick%20cuts.%20This%20level%20of%20attention%20to%20detail%20shows%20how%20much%20thought%20was%20put%20into%20this%20knife's%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224766%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20using%20a%20Steelport%20Bread%20Knife%20to%20cut%20a%20loaf%20of%20bread.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664629e99fc063e829b1c645%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223574%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDid%20we%20mention%20the%20Steelport%20Bread%20Knife%20can%20can%20be%20engraved%3F%20Not%20only%20does%20this%20make%20for%20a%20great%20personalized%20gift%2C%20but%20it%20also%20adds%20to%20the%20elegance%20of%20the%20overall%20design.%3Cp%3EM8nshot%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20impressive%20feature%20is%20this%20knife's%2065%20Rockwell%20Hardness%20Rating%20(HRC).%20According%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cafeleza.com%2Fabout%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAbout%2520Chef%2520Elizabeth%2520Mehditach%26amp%3Btext%3DHi%2520I%2527m%2520Chef%2520Elizabeth%2Clove%2520language%2520of%2520my%2520family.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Elizabeth%20Mehditach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20executive%20chef%20and%20founder%20of%20a%20Mediterranean%20catering%20company%20in%20L.A.%2C%20HRC%20is%20a%20method%20of%20determining%20a%20knife's%20hardness%20and%20how%20long%20it%20will%20maintain%20its%20sharp%20edge.%20She%20says%20that%20most%20kitchen%20knives%20range%20between%2050%20and%2065%20HRC%2C%20so%20having%20an%20HRC%20of%2065%20means%20this%20knife%20is%20incredibly%20durable%20and%20will%20stay%20sharp%20for%20longer.%20Of%20course%2C%20if%20you're%20in%20need%20of%20a%20knife%20tune-up%2C%20we%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-knife-sharpener%5C%22%3Ebest%20knife%20sharpeners%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20keep%20your%20tools%20in%20good%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20sourdough%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20sourdough%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20delicious%20as%20it%20is%2C%20sourdough%20is%20notoriously%20difficult%20to%20cut.%20So%20if%20your%20pandemic%20hobby%20was%20perfecting%20your%20boules%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20the%20best%20bread%20knife%20to%20handle%20its%20crust.%20The%20Made%20In%20Bread%20Knife's%20stainless%20steel%2C%20medium-sized%20teeth%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Hawkins%20advises%20is%20best%20for%20cutting%20bread%20without%20changing%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20loaf%20%E2%80%94%20offer%20a%20sharp%20tip%20for%20piercing%20through%20thick%20crusts%20that%20the%20other%20knives%20we%20tested%20just%20didn't%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20sourdough%20is%20no%20match%20for%20that%20sharpness%2C%20the%20tip%20does%20result%20in%20a%20less-than-smooth%20slice.%20No%20sandwich%20guts%20or%20tomato%20skins%20were%20crushed%2C%20but%20we%20found%20that%20the%20HexClad%20created%20a%20cleaner%20cut%20in%20those%20cases%20for%20a%20similar%20price%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20serrated%20knife%20from%20MadeIn%20cutting%20a%20tomato%20into%20thin%20slices.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643a57af27898f532d783ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMade%20In's%20knife%20has%20a%20sharp%20tip%20that%20helps%20to%20pierce%20stubborn%20crusts%20or%20the%20thick%20skin%20of%20a%20pineapple.%3Cp%3EM8nshot%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20appreciate%20the%20hearty%20handle%20on%20Made%20In's%20knife%2C%20which%20felt%20substantial%20in%20our%20hands%2C%20and%20the%20colorful%20handle%20options.%20It's%20not%20as%20professional%20looking%20as%2C%20say%2C%20the%20Shun%20or%20the%20Steelport%2C%20but%20you%20can%20match%20the%20handle%20to%20your%20other%20kitchen%20gadgets.%20There's%20a%20little%20room%20to%20be%20desired%20in%20the%20HRC%20department%20(clocking%20in%20at%2058)%2C%20but%20it%20should%20suffice%20for%20most%20home%20cooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20Japanese%5C%22%3EBest%20Japanese%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJapanese-style%20knives%20are%20known%20for%20having%20some%20of%20the%20best%20blades%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20Shun%20Classic%20Bread%20Knife%20is%20no%20exception.%20We%20found%20that%20the%20wide%20serrations%20on%20this%20blade%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20made%20of%2034%20layers%20of%20stainless%20Damascus%20steel%20%E2%80%94%20cut%20much%20easier%20and%20with%20far%20less%20pressure%20than%20others%20we%20tested.%20While%20Mehditach%20says%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20shallow%20blade%20with%20slightly%20rounded%20edges%20will%20offer%20more%20kitchen%20versatility%2C%20it%20likely%20won't%20be%20sharp%20enough%20for%20those%20tough%2C%20crusty%20loaves.%20But%20for%20softer%20breads%2C%20pastries%2C%20and%20even%20tomatoes%2C%20this%20knife%20cuts%20like%20a%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Using%20a%20Shun%20Bread%20Knife%20to%20slice%20into%20a%20tomato.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66463a699fc063e829b1d909%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shun%20Classic%20Bread%20Knife%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20lifetime%20warranty%2C%20which%20is%20always%20a%20plus%20when%20investing%20in%20high-quality%20kitchen%20tools.%3Cp%3EM8nshot%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20appreciate%20this%20knife's%20weight.%20It%20felt%20nice%20and%20heavy%20in%20our%20hands%2C%20with%20a%20comfortable%20ebony-finished%20Pakkawood%20handle%20that%20looks%20as%20good%20as%20it%20feels%20and%20doesn't%20harbor%20bacteria.%20However%2C%20some%20users%20may%20find%20that%20the%20weight%20distribution%20where%20the%20handle%20meets%20the%20blade%20is%20too%20uneven%20for%20their%20liking.%20Though%20not%20a%20dealbreaker%20(and%20definitely%20something%20you%20can%20get%20used%20to%20over%20time)%20it's%20worth%20noting%20for%20those%20who%20prefer%20a%20more%20balanced%20knife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20wish%20there%20was%20more%20info%20regarding%20its%20HRC%2C%20overall%2C%20this%20knife%20is%20a%20solid%20option%20for%20those%20who%20appreciate%20Japanese%20craftsmanship%20and%20sleek%20design.%20Shun%20also%20makes%20a%20set%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-steak-knives%5C%22%3Ebest%20steak%20knives%3C%2Fa%3E%20we've%20used%2C%20perfect%20for%20a%20wedding%20gift%20or%20treating%20a%20lucky%20meat%20eater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Other%20bread%20knives%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20bread%20knives%20we%20tested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20tested%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8fd8ce677b299c7082412a7d02cb6f1830aa8b5619ca12becfcc0ccd53a6f320%26postID%3D66450f8299ca5c3e84b2b91d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-bread-knife%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.quince.com%252Fhome%252Fclassic-japanese-damascus-steel-9-serrated-knife%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Quince%20Essential%20Japanese%20Damascus%20Steel%209%26quot%3B%20Serrated%20Bread%20Knife%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dae0b0d050e8bb35d0e0f42b45d3d53890a94802672492d4e266ca3202f88d042%26postID%3D66450f8299ca5c3e84b2b91d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-bread-knife%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmaterialkitchen.com%252Fproducts%252Fthe-serrated-6-knife%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Material%20Serrated%206%26quot%3B%20Knife%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20though%20they're%20both%20fairly%20priced%2C%20we%20found%20these%20knives%20to%20be%20too%20light.%20They%20also%20didn't%20do%20a%20good%20job%20of%20cutting%20through%20bread%20or%20tomatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20bread%20knife%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrip%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20with%20any%20kitchen%20utensil%2C%20a%20comfortable%20grip%20is%20essential.%20We%20noted%20the%20weight%20of%20each%20knife%20%E2%80%94%20too%20heavy%20can%20tire%20your%20hand%2C%20but%20too%20light%20may%20not%20give%20you%20enough%20control%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20it%20felt%20in%20our%20hands.%20A%20balanced%20knife%20makes%20all%20the%20difference%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20ease%20of%20use%20and%20precision%2C%20so%20Hawkins%20advises%20looking%20for%20the%20best%20bread%20knife%20that's%20also%20ergonomically%20designed%20and%20has%20an%20anti-slip%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESharpness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20want%20your%20bread%20knife%20to%20be%20sharp%20enough%20to%20slice%20through%20crusty%20loaves%20without%20crushing%20them.%20A%20serrated%20or%20scalloped%20edge%20is%20best%20for%20this%20type%20of%20cutting%2C%20as%20it%20helps%20grip%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20food%20better.%20We%20put%20each%20one%20through%20Hawkins'%20tomato%20test%20and%20noted%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20slid%20directly%20through%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20HRC%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Rockwell%20Hardness%20Rating%20(HRC)%20is%20a%20measure%20of%20how%20hard%20and%20durable%20the%20blade%20is.%20A%20high%20HRC%20rating%20means%20it's%20less%20likely%20to%20dull%20quickly%20and%20will%20retain%20its%20sharpness%20for%20longer.%20Look%20for%20a%20rating%20of%2055%20and%20above%20for%20the%20best%20bread%20knives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chef%20using%20a%20bread%20knife%20to%20cut%20through%20sandwich%20loaded%20with%20tomato%2C%20lettuce%2C%20and%20meat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664780d414fb5b23cc5dd5f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20analyzed%20the%20weight%20and%20how%20each%20knife%20felt%20in%20our%20hands%2C%20checking%20to%20see%20if%20it%20was%20overly%20heavy%2C%20cheaply%20made%2C%20or%20balanced%20and%20comfortable.%3Cp%3EM8nshot%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20wading%20through%20dozens%20of%20the%20best%20bread%20knives%2C%20we%20narrowed%20it%20down%20to%20the%20top%20ten.%20Then%20we%20put%20each%20one%20through%20three%20tests%20to%20see%20how%20well%20they%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBread%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20used%20each%20knife%20to%20cut%20through%20a%20loaf%20of%20bread%2C%20noting%20how%20many%20strokes%20it%20took%20and%20how%20much%20pressure%20we%20had%20to%20put%20on%20the%20knife.%20We%20also%20paid%20attention%20to%20how%20cleanly%20it%20cut%20through%20the%20crust%20and%20if%20it%20left%20any%20torn%20or%20jagged%20edges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETomato%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELike%20bread%2C%20tomatoes%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20cut%20through%20with%20a%20dull%20knife.%20We%20sliced%20a%20ripe%20tomato%20with%20each%20knife%2C%20taking%20note%20of%20how%20easily%20it%20pierced%20the%20skin%20and%20how%20cleanly%20it%20cut%20through%20without%20squishing%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESandwich%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFinally%2C%20we%20made%20sandwiches%20with%20each%20bread%20knife%20to%20see%20how%20well%20it%20handled%20the%20combination%20of%20bread%20and%20fillings%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20lettuce%2C%20and%20meats.%20We%20noted%20if%20the%20cut%20was%20clean%20and%20easy%20or%20if%20it%20tore%20through%20the%20ingredients%2C%20making%20a%20huge%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EBread%20knife%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20bread%20knives%20and%20serrated%20knives%20the%20same%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20some%20similarities%2C%20Hawkins%20says%20that%20bread%20knives%20tend%20to%20have%20longer%20blades%20than%20serrated%20knives.%20A%20longer%20blade%20can%20cover%20the%20width%20of%20large%2C%20oval%20shaped%20loaves%20instead%20of%20requiring%20multiple%20initial%20cuts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20should%20you%20use%20a%20serrated%20knife%20for%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHawkins%20likes%20to%20use%20serrated%20knives%20for%20not%20just%20slicing%20sandwiches%2C%20but%20also%20tough-to-cut%20fruit%20like%20pineapples.%20She%20also%20says%20they're%20great%20for%20cutting%20other%20starchy%20meals%20like%20burritos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-bread-knife%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715976433000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647935e20abc1efe8fb34ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-bread-knife%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20bread%20knives%20are%20versatile%20serrated%20blades%20that%20cut%20through%20thick%20crusts%20and%20delicate%20fruits%20with%20precision.%20Here%20are%20our%20top%20picks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Shannon%20Ullman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-bread-knife%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aditya%20makes%201st%20public%20appearance%20post%20breakup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715976302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110217577%2Cimgsize-83172.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faditya-roy-kapur-makes-first-public-appearance-after-breakup-with-ananya-panday%2Farticleshow%2F110217579.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110217579.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPost%20his%20breakup%20with%20Ananya%20Panday%2C%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%20was%20snapped%20by%20the%20paparazzi%20at%20Versova%20Jetty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3