TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fremember-hrithik-roshans-younger-brother-amit-aka-abhishek-sharma-from-kaho-naa-pyaar-hai-heres-how-he-looks-now-%2Farticleshow%2F110215587.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20PM's%20'Khata-Khat'%20Jibe%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20'Fata-Fatt'%20Response%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20Friday%20hit%20back%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20jibe%20at%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20said%20the%20public%20is%20now%20going%20to%20remove%20him%20from%20the%20top%20post%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Efata-fatt%2C%20fata-fatt%2C%20fata-fatt%3C%2Fem%3E%20(quickly)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20targeted%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20while%20addressing%20an%20INDIA%20bloc%20rally%20here%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Congress%20candidate%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20sister%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra.%20Former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20also%20joined%20the%20public%20meeting%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP%20and%20PM%20Modi)%20are%20saying%20that%20we%20will%20go%20abroad%2C%20but%20the%20people%20of%20our%20country%20are%20aware%2C%20they%20know%20that%20he%20(PM%20Modi)%20has%20sent%20his%20important%20people%20and%20friends%20abroad%20one%20after%20the%20other.%20His%20friends%2C%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%20fled%20abroad%20%3Cem%3E'khata-khat%20khata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(swiftly).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20drowning%20the%20country%20in%20debt%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20public%20is%20telling%20them%20that%20they%20will%20remove%20you%20%3Cem%3Efata-fatt%2C%20fata-fatt%2C%20fata-fatt%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20those%20who%20asserted%20they%20will%20not%20indulge%20in%20corruption%20themselves%20nor%20allow%20others%20to%20indulge%20in%20corruption%20(%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ena%20khaunga%2C%20na%20khane%20dunga%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B)%2C%20have%20swallowed%20everything%20and%20are%20saying%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bgata-gat%20gata-gat%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESab%20dakar%20gaye%20aur%20keh%20rahen%20hain%20gata-gat%20gata-gat.%3C%2Fem%3E%20(They%20have%20not%20even%20burped%20after%20devouring%20electoral%20bonds)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20disintegrate%20post-elections%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20will%20go%20abroad%20on%20a%20summer%20vacation%20'%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%2C%20khata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20the%20'%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%2C%20khata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E'%20phrase%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Fatehpur%20on%20Friday%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dreams%20of%20'panja'%20(Congress's%20poll%20symbol)%20and%20'cycle'%20(SP's%20poll%20symbol)%20have%20shattered%20'%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%2C%20khata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20Now%20they%20are%20planning%20for%20post-June%204%20as%20to%20who%20should%20be%20blamed%20for%20the%20defeat%20'%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%2C%20khata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20And%2C%20someone%20was%20telling%20me%20that%20tickets%20for%20foreign%20trips%20have%20also%20been%20booked%20'%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%2C%20khata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20jibe%20came%20in%20response%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20often%20using%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%20khata-khat%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20claim%20that%20a%20fixed%20stipend%20would%20flow%20into%20the%20accounts%20of%20poor%20women%20if%20his%20party%20comes%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20PM%20Modi%20without%20taking%20his%20name%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20at%20his%20rally%20on%20Friday%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20very%20big%20leader%20of%20the%20country%20who%20feigns%20a%20relationship%20with%20every%20place%20he%20goes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20towards%20the%20crowd%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20them%20also%20see%20and%20hear%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhiji's%20true%20relationship%20is%20with%20Raebareli.%20If%20'Ra'%20is%20for%20Raebareli%20then%20'Ra'%20is%20also%20for%20Rahul.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20do%20not%20understand%20counting%20should%20also%20understand%20that%20one%20plus%20one%20has%20become%2011%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20become%20nau%20do%20gyaraha%20(fled).%20Those%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20four%20phases%20of%20elections%20know%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20defeated%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20aim%20at%20MLA%20Manoj%20Pandey%2C%20who%20left%20the%20SP%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20heard%20that%20our%20second%20traitor%20has%20also%20gone%20there%20(to%20BJP).%20One%20speciality%20of%20the%20fraudster%20who%20has%20just%20gone%20there%20is%20that%20wherever%20he%20goes%2C%20he%20digs%20a%20hole.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey%2C%20who%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20during%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20Raebareli%20on%20Friday%20and%20sat%20next%20to%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20stage.%20Recently%20Shah%20had%20also%20visited%20his%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20fifth%20phase%20in%20Raebareli%20on%20May%2020%2C%20where%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20state%20minister%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20against%20Congress'%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20publ