ou%20can%20read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbreville-barista-express-review%5C%22%3EBreville%20Barista%20Express%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbreville-barista-express-impress-review%5C%22%3EBreville%20Barista%20Express%20Impress%20review%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Note%3A%20While%20testing%20the%20machine%20out%20with%20old%2C%20stale%20beans%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20more%20affordable%2C%20and%20some%20of%20us%20will%20inevitably%20use%20them%20%E2%80%94%20I%20called%20Breville's%20customer%20assistance%20and%20left%20them%20with%20my%20number%2C%20not%20letting%20them%20know%20who%20I%20was.%20A%20call%20came%20back%20within%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20a%20representative%20walked%20me%20through%20making%20these%20finer%20adjustments%20with%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20grace%20and%20patience.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portafilter%20you%20see%20directly%20above%20and%20below%20was%20only%20temporarily%20included%20with%20the%20Barista%20Pro%2C%20and%20the%20original%20portafilter%20also%20included%20with%20the%20Express%2C%20which%20we%20find%20works%20better%2C%20is%20now%20what%20you'll%20get%20with%20the%20Pro%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETamper%20and%20leveling%20tool%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20putting%20espresso%20grounds%20into%20a%20gasket%20for%20the%20Breville%20Barista%20Pro%20machine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d9e0a8c3b33a747631e77f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20beautiful%2C%20ergonomic%20tamper%20if%20we%20ever%20saw%20one.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Slotnick%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20tip%20our%20hats%20to%20Breville's%20research%20and%20design%20team.%20Espresso%20nerds%20everywhere%20praise%20this%20tamper%20not%20just%20because%20it's%20real%20and%20heavy%20steel%2C%20but%20because%20it's%20magnetic%20and%20fits%20tidily%20into%20a%20slot%20beside%20the%20grinder%20so%20you%20never%20misplace%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20only%20bone%20to%20pick%20here%20is%20that%20the%20portafilter%20measures%2054mm%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20commercially%20standard%2058mm%2C%20so%20if%20you%20want%20to%20upgrade%20baskets%20or%20the%20portafilter%20itself%2C%20you'll%20be%20stuck%20with%20Breville%20or%20the%20few%20after-market%20brands%20that%20design%20products%20specifically%20for%20Breville%20machines.%20Still%2C%20this%20is%20part%20of%20what%20keeps%20the%20machine%20so%20compact.%20(Check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-tamper%5C%22%3Ebest%20tampers%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20you%20want%20to%20learn%20more.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreville's%20machines%20also%20come%20with%20their%20proprietary%20Razor%2C%20a%20precision%20leveling%20tool.%20It's%20something%20many%20baristas%20will%20argue%20is%20even%20more%20important%20than%20tamping.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5LWrVUD22gQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHere's%20a%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Breville%20on%20how%20it%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAccessories%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227068%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20array%20of%20accessories%20that%20come%20along%20with%20the%20Breville%20Barista%20Pro%20on%20a%20butcher-block%20counter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e29f7727e5db0018ee9725%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225301%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20machine%20comes%20with%20essential%20accessories%20like%20four%20portafilter%20baskets%20(single-walled%20and%20dual-walled%20in%20both%20single%20and%20double%20shots)%20and%20the%20Razor%20leveling%20tool.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portafilter%20baskets%20are%20expertly%20designed%20so%20that%20they%20empty%20swiftly%20and%20tidily%2C%20even%20if%20you%20forget%20to%20do%20so%20for%20a%20few%20days%20%E2%80%94%20something%20many%20other%20designs%20fail%20to%20do.%20They're%20also%20made%20of%20high-enough%20grade%20metal%20that%20they%20don't%20tarnish%20and%20scratch%20only%20minimally%20if%20you%20do%20find%20yourself%20having%20to%20dig%20out%20grounds%20(though%20it's%20best%20not%20to%20use%20metal%20with%20them%20if%20you%20can%20help%20it).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Razor%2C%20as%20mentioned%20above%2C%20is%20also%20a%20nice%20touch%20to%20help%20even%20out%20the%20grounds%20before%20tamping%20(though%20some%20experts%20recommend%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_100919_breville-barista-pro-20%26h%3D5ad24f0ae814d608e41478de6d8b86333fe50fe5a625a230e1451317055ac157%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42937%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbreville-barista-pro-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FEspresso-Coffee-Grounds-Stirring-Distributor%252Fdp%252FB09ZYW1J4G%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWDT%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead).%20The%20milk-frothing%20pitcher%20isn't%20our%20favorite%20design%20(the%20spout%20could%20be%20more%20pronounced)%2C%20but%20it%20works%20well%20besides%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cleaning%20tablets%20work%20with%20the%20backwash%20disc%20to%20clean%20from%20the%20front%20end%20of%20the%20group%20head%20(where%20the%20hot%20water%20is%20delivered%20to%20the%20portafilter)%2C%20and%20while%20there%20is%20a%20single%20packet%20of%20descaling%20powder%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20stock%20if%20the%20stuff%20(like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_100919_breville-barista-