ss-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-fines-rs-8-lakh-on-reliance-home-finance-for-disclosure-lapses-124051701487_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fine%20has%20to%20be%20paid%20within%2045%20days%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchanges%20Board%20of%20India%20(Sebi)%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-fines-rs-8-lakh-on-reliance-home-finance-for-disclosure-lapses-124051701487_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-fines-rs-8-lakh-on-reliance-home-finance-for-disclosure-lapses-124051701487_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-fines-rs-8-lakh-on-reliance-home-finance-for-disclosure-lapses-124051701487_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress'%20Maoist%20Manifesto%20Eyeing%20Gold%20From%20Temples%2C%20Mangalsutra%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20tore%20into%20the%20Congress's%20election%20manifesto%2C%20dubbing%20it%20a%20%26quot%3BMaoist%26quot%3B%20document%2C%20which%20he%20cautioned%20will%20put%20a%20break%20on%20the%20country's%20economic%20growth%20and%20lead%20it%20to%20bankruptcy%20if%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20if%20the%20Congress%20was%20dissolved%20post-independence%20as%20per%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20wishes%2C%20India%20would%20have%20been%20five%20decades%20ahead%20in%20terms%20of%20social%20and%20economic%20development%20than%20what%20it%20was%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Mumbai%20three%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20fifth%20and%20last%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra%20covering%2013%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20stalwart%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20election%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20is%20fighting%20a%20battle%20for%20its%20survival%20and%20can%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20(to%20save%20itself).%20Its%20Maoist%20manifesto%20is%20eyeing%20gold%20from%20temples%20and%20'mangalsutra'%20(gold%20chains)%20of%20women.%20The%20Maoist%20manifesto%20will%20put%20a%20break%20on%20economic%20growth%20and%20lead%20the%20country%20to%20bankruptcy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20gathering%20at%20the%20sprawling%20Shivaji%20Park%20Ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20Congress%20poll%20document%20had%20Muslim%20League%20imprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20star%20campaigner%20alleged%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20wants%20to%20bring%20back%20inheritance%20tax%20(a%20levy%20on%20assets%20inherited%20from%20a%20deceased%20person)%20which%20was%20abolished%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20plans%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20inheritance%20tax...%20the%20party%20is%20planning%20an%20X-ray%20of%20your%20property%20and%20handing%20it%20over%20to%20their%20vote-bank%20which%20speaks%20of%20vote%20jihad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20stalwart%20said%20construction%20of%20a%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20provided%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20were%20once%20considered%20impossible%20tasks%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20they%20have%20now%20become%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20they%20were%20made%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20power%20of%20your%20single%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20large%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20asked%20the%20people%20of%20Mumbai%20to%20remember%20terror%20strikes%20and%20serial%20bomb%20blasts%20that%20rocked%20the%20metropolis%20in%20the%20past%20and%20the%20change%20in%20the%20situation%20after%202014%20when%20they%20go%20out%20to%20vote%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20bomb%20blasts%20and%20terror%20strikes%20are%20a%20now%20thing%20of%20the%20past%20in%20the%20financial%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20they%20(Mumbaikars)%20have%20been%20feeling%20safe%20and%20secure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said%20at%20the%20rally%20organised%20to%20seek%20votes%20for%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20candidates%20in%20the%20metropolis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%2C%20PM%20Modi%20maintained%20the%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B%20Shiv%20Sena%20had%20betrayed%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20people%20and%20worked%20against%20the%20interest%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nakli%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20betrayed%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%20by%20standing%20with%20those%20who%20abuse%20Ram%20mandir%20and%20also%20(Hindutva%20icon%20Veer)%20Savarkar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20give%20Mumbai%20its%20due%20right.%20Days%20are%20not%20far%20off%20when%20Mumbai%20will%20get%20India's%20first%20bullet%20train%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20noted%20the%20financial%20capital%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20hub%20of%20start-ups.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20there%20are%208%2C000%20start-ups%20in%20Mumbai.%20India%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20mobile%20manufacturing%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMumbai%20is%20the%20economic%20powerhouse%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20stock%20market%20headquartered%20in%20the%20metropolis%20is%20now%20the%20fourth%20largest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20the%20INDI%20alliance%20is%20hatching%20conspiracies%20to%20break%20the%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20said%20Mumbai%20was%20a%20dream%20city%20and%20was%20going%20to%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20achieving%20the%20goal%20of%20a%20developed%20India%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20to%20you%20with%20a%20dream%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20(developed%20India).%20Mumbai%20knows%20the%20importance%20of%20speed.%20Countries%20which%20gained%20independence%20along%20with%20us%20have%20overtaken%20us%20in%20terms%20of%20development.%20Where%20did%20we%20lag%3F%20It%20was%20the%20previous%20governments%20which%20did%20not%20trust%20its%20people.%20If%20you%20see%20the%20Red%20Fort%20address%20of%20earlier%20PMs%2C%20they%20called%20Indians%20lazy.%20Such%20attitude%20cannot%20take%20the%20country%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Congress%20lost%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202014%2C%20India's%20economy%20was%20at%20the%2011th%20position%2C%20but%20it%20has%20now%20jumped%20to%20the%205th%20spot%2C%20PM%20Modi%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20was%20dissolved%20as%20per%20Gandhiji's%20wishes%2C%20India%20would%20have%20been%20five%20decades%20ahead%20of%20what%20it%20is%20today.%20We%20lost%20five%20decades%20because%20of%20the%20Congress.%20When%20we%20got%20independence%2C%20India%20was%20the%206th%20largest%20economy%20and%20when%20the%20Congress%20left%20power%20in%202014%2C%20it%20was%2011th%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndians%20fought%20for%20500%20years%20to%20build%20a%20magnificent%20temple%20for%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Frustrated%20people%20and%20those%20in%20despair%20also%20said%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%20was%20impossible%2C%20but%20it%20was%20scrapped.%20No%20power%20in%20the%20world%20can%20bring%20back%20Article%20370%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20women's%20welfare%2C%20the%20PM%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20practice%20of%20instant%20triple%20talaq%20has%20been%20banned%20and%20women%20have%20got%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20in%20assemblies%20and%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20earlier%20'garibi%20hatao'%20(eradicate%20poverty)%20was%20merely%20a%20slogan%2C%20but%20for%20his%20government%20action%20on%20the%20ground%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20brought%2025%20crore%20people%20out%20of%20poverty%20(in%2010%20years).%20What%20seemed%20impossible%20was%20done%20with%20the%20power%20of%20your%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20maintained%20the%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20NCP%20(SP)%20president%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20challenge%20the%20NCP%20leader%20to%20ask%20(Congress%20MP)%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20say%20he%20will%20not%20abuse%20Savarkar%20again.%20The%20INDI%20alliance%20has%20betrayed%20the%20country%20by%20giving%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20terrorist%20Ajmal%20Kasab%20and%20questioning%20surgical%20strikes.%20It%20wants%20to%20snatch%20SC%2FST%2FOBC%20quota%20and%20give%20it%20those%20who%20speak%20of%20vote%20Jihad.%26quot%3B%20Thirteen%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20including%206%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20will%20vote%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715967000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fjo0h4fc_pm-modi-mumbai-rally_625x300_17_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-maoist-manifesto-eyeing-gold-from-temples-mangalsutra-pm-modi-5686689%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20tore%20into%20the%20Congress's%20election%20manifesto%2C%20dubbing%20it%20a%20%26quot%3BMaoist%26quot%3B%20document%2C%20which%20he%20cautioned%20will%20put%20a%20break%20on%20the%20country's%20economic%20growth%20and%20lead%20it%20to%20bankruptcy%20if%20implemented.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-maoist-manifesto-eyeing-gold-from-temples-mangalsutra-pm-modi-5686689%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.