3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20tried%20to%20rescue%20their%20bleeding%20businesses%2C%20they%20were%20faced%20with%20dire%20financial%20situations%2C%20which%20escalated%20in%202016-17.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%20to%20pay%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20school%20fees%2C%20and%20had%20to%20borrow%20money%20for%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20they%20ever%20consider%20quitting%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%E2%80%9D%20comes%20the%20answer%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20quit%20a%20corporate%20career%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20back.%20We%20just%20had%20a%20sliver%20of%20hope%20that%20we%20stretched%2C%20leading%20us%20here%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20money%20and%20bills%20piling%20up%20at%20home%2C%20the%20duo%20picked%20up%20consulting%20jobs%20to%20ensure%20some%20cash%20flow%20at%20home.%20Another%20facet%20adding%20to%20their%20woes%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20related%2C%20with%20many%20advising%20them%20not%20to%20do%20business%20together%2C%20as%20it%20may%20sour%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20kept%20at%20it%2C%20as%20they%20were%20sure%20of%20their%20vision%20%E2%80%94%20making%20people%20realise%20the%20importance%20of%20health%20before%20it%20gets%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20challenges%20continued%20even%20as%20True%20Elements%20picked%20up%2C%20as%20an%20investor%20hung%20them%20dry%20just%20before%20the%20lockdown%20in%20March%202020.%20By%20this%20time%20they%20had%20over%20100%20employees%20and%20salaries%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20principle%2C%20we%20are%20true%20to%20our%20employees%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20cut%20salaries.%20But%20COVID-19%20was%20a%20tough%20time%20as%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money.%20We%20asked%20our%20employees%20personally%20as%20to%20who%20would%20be%20okay%20with%20a%20deferment%20of%20salary%2C%20and%20we%20were%20just%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20response.%20Their%20wholehearted%20willingness%20and%20trust%20in%20us%20pulled%20us%20through%20and%20we%20paid%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20salaries%20in%20the%20next%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20share%20that%20during%20every%20crisis%2C%20it%20is%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20that%20has%20kept%20them%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20brand%20that%20will%20outlive%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20idea%20of%20creating%20their%20own%20brand%20was%20so%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20value%20to%20people%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20outliving%20the%20founders.%20This%20led%20to%20Marico%20acquiring%20about%2054%25%20equity%20stake%20in%20the%20company%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22True%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-300x291.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-500x484.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-768x744.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-150x145.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350256%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrue%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20choose%20a%20partner%20who%20would%20align%20with%20our%20vision%20and%20understand%20health.%20We%20both%20were%20also%20clear%2C%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20would%20outlive%20us.%20This%20acquisition%20would%20help%20our%20objective%20come%20true%20and%20make%20%E2%80%98True%20Elements%E2%80%99%20a%20household%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20COO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20competitive%20healthy%20food%20space%2C%20the%20founders%20believe%20that%20their%20differentiation%20lies%20in%20the%20transparency%20with%20regard%20to%20their%20products.%20All%20their%20products%20have%20complete%20ingredients%20listed%20behind%20them%20and%20an%20option%20to%20trace%20the%20ingredient%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20farm%20to%20fork%20on%20their%20website%20using%20the%20product%20name%20and%20batch%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20share%20that%20their%20startup%20rests%20on%20four%20pillars%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CTrue%20to%20our%20food%20(nutrition)%2C%20true%20to%20our%20word%20(transparency)%2C%20true%20to%20our%20planet%20(recycle)%2C%20and%20true%20to%20our%20families%20(people).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20completely%20honest%20about%20what%20we%20put%20in%20our%20products%20by%20naming%20it%20all%20on%20the%20pack.%20We%20ensure%20that%20we%20even%20mention%20ingredients%20that%20aren%E2%80%99t%20compulsory%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20stand%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20a%20plastic-neutral%20brand%2C%20wherein%20all%20the%20plastic%20that%20they%20are%20using%20is%20recycled.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20process%20about%2030%20percent%20directly%2C%20while%20we%20have%20a%20partner%20who%20processes%20the%20remaining.%20It%20is%20converted%20into%20biofuel%20and%20supplied%20to%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20Elements%20is%20a%20certified%20%E2%80%98Clean%20Label%E2%80%99%20brand%