f%20having%20an%20education%20abroad%20to%20setting%20foot%20at%20NASA%20as%20a%20full-time%20employee%20took%20her%20almost%2015%20years.%20But%20this%2035-year-old%20is%20making%20it%20easy%20for%20others%20by%20sharing%20her%20experiences%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20mentoring%20them.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20her%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIn%20pursuit%20of%20the%20universe%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshata%20works%20as%20a%20Principal%20Investigator%20and%20Space%20Systems%20Engineer%20at%20NASA%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%20(JPL)%20on%20two%20space%20missions.%20She%20is%20the%20mission%20science%20phase%20lead%20on%20the%20NASA-ISRO%20Synthetic%20Aperture%20Radar%20mission%20(NISAR)%20and%20robotics%20systems%20engineer%20on%20the%20MARS%202020%20Perseverance%20rover%2C%20operating%20the%20rover%20on%20MARS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lifelong%20tryst%20with%20space%20took%20roots%20at%20an%20airshow%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%202003.%20It%20was%20the%20Aero%20India%20show%20at%20the%20Yelahanka%20air%20force%20base%20that%20perhaps%20started%20it%20all.%20The%20aerobatic%20manoeuvres%20of%20the%20Sukhoi%20Su-30%20pilots%20left%20the%20youngster%20captivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFwPOzvr0oxQ%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22C0159%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20science%20and%20maths%20and%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319013%2Fiit-madras-graduates-startup-