.%20But%20nobody%20could%20commit%20anything%20to%20me%20without%20a%20green%20card%20as%20it%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20and%20complexity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20day%20of%20her%20internship%20arrived%20but%20she%20still%20had%20no%20job%20offers%20or%20interviews.%20Luckily%2C%20she%20had%20a%20presentation%20to%20give%20that%20day.%20A%20hiring%20manager%20in%20the%20audience%20was%20impressed%20with%20Akshata%E2%80%99s%20presentation%20and%20decided%20to%20give%20her%20a%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20then%2C%20till%20the%20paperwork%20came%20through%2C%20the%20scientist%20recalls%20that%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20breathe%20easy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20entered%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323066%2Fchandrayaan-3-the-history-of-how-india-began-one-of-its-most-significant-space-journeys%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENASA%20JPL%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20employee%20in%20February%202020%2C%20that%20was%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20days%20of%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Akshata%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20surely%20inspirational%2C%20we%20ask%2C%20what%20kept%20her%20going%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20adamant%20about%20getting%20into%20NASA%20and%20doing%20whatever%20it%20took%20to%20reach%20that%20goal.%20There%20was%20no%20plan%20B.%20I%20decided%20to%20bet%20on%20myself.%20Failure%20was%20not%20an%20option%2C%20but%20even%20so%2C%20everytime%20I%20failed%2C%20I%20took%20the%20learnings%20from%20it%2C%20and%20did%20something%20different%20to%20proceed%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20that%20thousands%20of%20students%20in%20India%20need%20appropriate%20guidance%2C%20she%20started%20channels%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fastro.akshata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%2